  ### ANSIBLE COMMANDS:

ansible   -b  -m yum -a 'pkg=elinks state=installed update_cache=true use_backend=yum' vijaythilak4c.mylabserver.com -K

-b = become 
-K = will ask sudo passwd
-k = will ask ssh passwd




